1.1.2.name: wordpress/stripefolio
1.1.2.description: Stripefolio is a free clean WordPress theme designed to function both as a readable blog and website as well as a fullscreen portfolio showcase for designers, painters, artists, photographers, etc. Have a look at the live demo!
